<figureCitation box="[159,272,464,490]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1944,1968]" captionTargetBox="[151,1418,684,1901]" captionTargetId="figure-170@2.[151,1436,684,1920]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Main characters of the genus Axinoscymnus Kamiya: a–h Axinoscymnus pingxiangicus Peng et Chen, sp. n.: a head b prothorax, ventral view c prothorax, frontal view d hind leg e labium f antenna g maxilla h mandible i–j Axinoscymnus beneficus Kamiya, 1963: i spermatheca j coxites. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6651159" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6651159/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="451">Figs 1a–h</figureCitation>
